  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "QUAL 8155 平台以实现仪表屏幕Telltale 显示监控功能，但其是否支持大屏Telltale显示监控功能呢？"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "为验证该功能，执行了以下测试，本文为此过程的记录。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Test Environment"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Hw Version: CHERY T1J  B0(QUAL 8155)",
        "SOC & SCC SW Version:",
        "Test tool"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ubwc.zip"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "2. Test case 1"
